{"tid":1138153,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"六年前大埔慘烈降班，upset春喊住同球迷道歉","createTime":"2019-05-04T10:44:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-06T15:42:43.000Z","uid":72476,"like":134,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"18d635dbda4c370456147d2517e2207848ccd7d0","tid":1138153,"uid":72476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T10:44:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/eglG-Fwsqyo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FeglG-Fwsqyo&d=u%2FngHNJi%2FtIBC1CiWprX8QexVh8qxZHot2w31qr30Zg%3D&h=3d822236\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/eglG-Fwsqyo</a><br />\n<br />\n當日既情況仲歷歷在目<br />\n大埔一支冇歷史既地區球隊打上甲組<br />\n拎足總盃踢亞協<br />\n以區隊黎講係好夢幻既事<br />\n到2013年因為些微差距降班<br />\n但佢地冇好似某傳統班霸咁無恥地接受挽留<br />\n反而係乙組（當時未叫港超聯）重新打過<br />\n3年後升返上頂級聯賽<br />\n上季拎到亞協資格殺出香港<br />\n今季更加成為第一支拎港超聯既地區球隊<br />\n成個故事真係好夢幻，好勵志<br />\n希望香港球迷除左睇英超歐聯之外<br />\n由今日起可以多d留意我地自己既足球<br />\n多d留意我地既地區球隊，元朗、南區等<br />\n當然仲有今日為香港足球守護住民族尊嚴既和富大埔！"},{"pid":"b9835fee781d9d9fd145ac2360c80aee8473259a","tid":1138153,"uid":13395,"like":5,"dislike":15,"score":-10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T10:44:53.000Z","msg":"我都唔係住大埔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"943db92f72e96e73825513830f2be2ed3fceeab7","tid":1138153,"uid":33053,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T10:44:59.000Z","msg":"大埔人唔再upset<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3826c03e2ee7d60d9d5766abb8f872b4a04008db","tid":1138153,"uid":53774,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T10:49:45.000Z","msg":"南華食撚屎"},{"pid":"ccf89e8f31e1cb6f85f37f11b26a739ba9ae5c09","tid":1138153,"uid":72476,"like":36,"dislike":1,"score":35,"quote":{"pid":"b9835fee781d9d9fd145ac2360c80aee8473259a","tid":1138153,"uid":13395,"like":5,"dislike":15,"score":-10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T10:44:53.000Z","msg":"我都唔係住大埔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T10:50:15.000Z","msg":"我住元朗<br />\n次次大埔作客打晒交我都屌到佢地開花<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但一支地區球隊打到拎冠軍，其實好值得其他區隊借鏡<br />\n希望黎緊港超會多d區隊<br />\n少d唔知邊度走出黎既凱景、駿其<br />\n建立自己既球迷群<br />\n咁香港足球先有望復甦"},{"pid":"aa7b99a8ada770ddfc88d894f86324fe6256b338","tid":1138153,"uid":19847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T10:52:55.000Z","msg":"寶春蛇19/5過嚟一齊慶祝啦<br />\n咁咪唔upset lor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0f5271b781f1a68671bd628574237fa43488727","tid":1138153,"uid":28155,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T11:03:44.000Z","msg":"當年佢搵唔少<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d225aa0541a0f490df2d18f12cc60bbf6fe31a44","tid":1138153,"uid":212646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T11:51:08.000Z","msg":"第一支奪冠區隊唔係元朗？"},{"pid":"cbb127089bcbb21606c973c45d031fbd0f004e94","tid":1138153,"uid":42626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T11:53:23.000Z","msg":"upset完下季教南華<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbfe058a2323c2c07031126b83b9bae86a73f59b","tid":1138153,"uid":3747,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d225aa0541a0f490df2d18f12cc60bbf6fe31a44","tid":1138153,"uid":212646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T11:51:08.000Z","msg":"第一支奪冠區隊唔係元朗？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T12:03:56.000Z","msg":"港超唔係"},{"pid":"47f0a48678969c4203c43dc77c7ebdca19d6a8f8","tid":1138153,"uid":72476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d225aa0541a0f490df2d18f12cc60bbf6fe31a44","tid":1138153,"uid":212646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit